{"tid":724902,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"流行歌速成班","createTime":"2018-07-01T10:08:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-07T10:51:16.000Z","uid":147789,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4430ea102ad92b6c44b0ea526ec089b1ec9d605e","tid":724902,"uid":147789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T10:08:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">序</div></span></span></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n呢個post會教啲好基本嘅知識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n主要講下一首歌由咩組成 和弦點樣進行<br />\n同埋唔同地方嘅歌有啲咩主流嘅chord<br />\n希望大家除咗聽旋律同歌詞之外<br />\n都可以欣賞下首歌嘅其他地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又或者係睇清一啲作曲家嘅真正實力<br />\n<del>講到好似勁啲咁</del><br />\n<br />\n另外戴返頭盔先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小弟係自學鋼琴同結他<br />\n都係自己研究下啲流行曲咁<br />\n講勁真係有排都稱唔上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連登音樂家們屌細力啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以除咗我教到你地一啲小知識之外<br />\n希望你地可以教返我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">小弟返工長時長 未必更新得快 有時間我會盡快更新</span></span>"},{"pid":"2aa7ab3815c75b68eda45bb89b3b2dc04d8bba94","tid":724902,"uid":181326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T10:09:18.000Z","msg":"開始未？"},{"pid":"a2e8a98fa030da0362134792b84d80bb025f1f7a","tid":724902,"uid":147789,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T10:14:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>第一堂</strong></div></span></span><br />\n喺作曲之前 你要知道嘅係<br />\n一首歌嘅組成 除咗你平時哼出嚟嘅旋律之外<br />\n仲有樂器嘅伴奏 和聲<br />\n同最重要嘅chord 亦係所謂嘅和弦<br />\n<br />\n如果用人嚟代表一首歌嘅話<br />\n旋律 = 皮膚/外表<br />\n伴奏 = 內涵/性格<br />\n和弦進行 = 骨架<br />\n內涵用嚟突顯你嘅特點 而骨架就決定你嘅外表<br />\n聽歌同睇人都係一樣 都係睇外表先<br />\n你可能會諗<br />\n點解聽得到旋律 但係就聽唔到和弦呢<br />\n咁係因為和弦比旋律細聲之餘 仲普遍好低音<br />\n人類耳仔最敏感嘅frequency range係~5k-7k<br />\n所以我地會prefer去聽旋律<br />\n就好似我地出街嘅視線會比靚仔/女吸引住咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔會去留意啲豬排<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用首多人聽過又易入手嘅廣東歌為例：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tSHVPxO2tbo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FtSHVPxO2tbo&d=R2cxRVh4lUvNNuaWy%2FjklkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=2b0b1b8a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tSHVPxO2tbo</a><br />\n<br />\n旋律 唔使講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果聽唔到有人唱嘅話你可以正皮上一頁喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n伴奏就主要係鋼琴 鼓 同埋啲電子音<br />\n咁唔知你又聽唔聽到首歌隱藏咗啲低音喺底呢？<br />\n其實呢啲低音就係和弦喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n普遍嚟講 <br />\n每四拍就會接落下一個和弦 如此類推<br />\n喺前奏嘅地方 和弦比較易聽到<br />\n頭20秒係用鋼琴彈出嚟<br />\n之後嗰20秒係用電子音整出嚟<br />\n<br />\n喺第一堂完之前考下你<br />\n刀削麵嘅呢首歌嘅和弦<br />\n係每四拍移高一個和弦 定係移下呢？"},{"pid":"3fb42a5106f8a12b58d80d4f258308f3d7642193","tid":724902,"uid":147789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T10:16:03.000Z","msg":"如果有興趣嘅巴絲 不妨留個言講下你嘅意見？<br />\n有人睇嘅話我就會<del>慢慢</del>持續更新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a32d8185d0aa3ac0aa5c3334d85a3e73862166cd","tid":724902,"uid":181326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T10:23:01.000Z","msg":"請"},{"pid":"3eb2c7fc14fbd3f2ab4b81dfbb2df928aeab5a50","tid":724902,"uid":181326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T10:23:17.000Z","msg":"再請"},{"pid":"5c339602f0fb31ec4fd0950c41dc5ee615f48331","tid":724902,"uid":105863,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T10:38:21.000Z","msg":"純粹分享下，人耳個frequency response係1kHz - 5kHz最sensitive會比較正確<br />\n<br />\n下面張圖叫fletcher-munson equal loudness contour，係兩個科學家請d白老鼠返黎研究下人耳對唔同frequency既sensitivity<br />\n條紅線係指實驗參加者聽出黎一樣咁大聲<br />\n而左面係指嗰d聲音本身既能量係幾多<br />\n呢張圖想講既就係人耳會覺得1kHz - 5kHz既聲音會比低頻同高頻大聲，即使實際上係同樣音量(能量)都好<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.customanalogue.com/elsinore/elsinore_images/Fletcher-Munson_700W.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.customanalogue.com%2Felsinore%2Felsinore_images%2FFletcher-Munson_700W.gif&h=7ee91d7d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53fb84b4901a1a34fa6201db67e2e116527d1111","tid":724902,"uid":105863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T10:40:18.000Z","msg":"btw十卜樓主ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59768984099eb7caf378f1d63ebf26b46e521125","tid":724902,"uid":147789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c339602f0fb31ec4fd0950c41dc5ee615f48331","tid":724902,"uid":105863,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T10:38:21.000Z","msg":"純粹分享下，人耳個frequency response係1kHz - 5kHz最sensitive會比較正確<br />\n<br />\n下面張圖叫fletcher-munson equal loudness contour，係兩個科學家請d白老鼠返黎研究下人耳對唔同frequency既sensitivity<br />\n條紅線係指實驗參加者聽出黎一樣咁大聲<br />\n而左面係指嗰d聲音本身既能量係幾多<br />\n呢張圖想講既就係人耳會覺得1kHz - 5kHz既聲音會比低頻同高頻大聲，即使實際上係同樣音量(能量)都好<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.customanalogue.com/elsinore/elsinore_images/Fletcher-Munson_700W.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.customanalogue.com%2Felsinore%2Felsinore_images%2FFletcher-Munson_700W.gif&h=7ee91d7d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T11:02:33.000Z","msg":"唔該晒你嘅解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前上堂聽過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6da9ee6fc6c00fbf28138033a35617de64d8300","tid":724902,"uid":147789,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T11:32:29.000Z","msg":"係咪冇咩人有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"786a45351e138a5d977558dfc2727880769ac75a","tid":724902,"uid":54995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6da9ee6fc6c00fbf28138033a35617de64d8300","tid":724902,"uid":147789,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T11:32:29.000Z","msg":"係咪冇咩人有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T11:37:39.000Z","msg":"想睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aac45e091afda0e81cfe2da3bf20dd9f6cebbbd","tid":724902,"uid":146624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6da9ee6fc6c00fbf28138033a35617de64d8300","tid":724902,"uid":147789,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T11:32:29.000Z","msg":"係咪冇咩人有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T16:11:17.000Z","msg":"唔好比佢停<br />\n加速<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92ab30281fdd4f453bd0e2ce90cdf3aad24c5db0","tid":724902,"uid":149877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T16:26:25.000Z","msg":"留名學習"},{"pid":"c48ac86cbc9acc6070445c872f6d6d3ba64bb37a","tid":724902,"uid":2917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T21:00:19.000Z","msg":"想學 推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ba86f9e84b971c0c8413752861ea59fd7c409d","tid":724902,"uid":130597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T21:22:06.000Z","msg":"lm support"},{"pid":"2664457d7fb8a087620ef79a35088c768862fa9c","tid":724902,"uid":125943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T21:28:13.000Z","msg":"想學，會唔會講編曲。利申學咗幾年琴但流行曲咩都唔識"},{"pid":"9ca80ab5da699663b8ee386b11979c1bc6ea513d","tid":724902,"uid":147789,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T00:36:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">第二堂</span></strong></div></span><br />\n上完第一堂 應該有部分人諗緊乜野係和弦<br />\n好多人對chord嘅認知<br />\n就係major同minor <br />\nmajor就係開心嘅 係精神嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nminor就係唔開心囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁講唔可以話你錯嘅 但係真係好虛無縹緲囉<br />\n<br />\n其實一個和弦普遍係由三粒音組成嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSofa name小學都有教啦<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Do</span> <span style=\"color: purple;\">Ra</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">Mi</span> <span style=\"color: purple;\">Fa</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">So</span> <span style=\"color: purple;\">La</span> <span style=\"color: purple;\">Ti</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">Do</span><br />\n未聽過嘅你就砍掉重練啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實當你淨係唱上面紅色嘅sofa name <br />\n你就已經唱咗個chord出嚟架啦 <br />\n<br />\n<em>基本Chord係由Do Mi So組成</em><br />\n<em>基本Chord係由Do Mi So組成</em><br />\n<em>基本Chord係由Do Mi So組成</em><br />\n因為好重要同陣間會再提 所以要講三次~<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/01/183327_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F01%2F183327_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=303ff0a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁major同minor嘅分別呢？<br />\n以常用嘅C調為例<br />\nC D E F G A B C就等如do ra mi fa so la ti do啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/01/184227_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F01%2F184227_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=a1f4af76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n正正常常嘅就已經係一個major scale<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁如果你要取入面三個音出嚟做和弦 <br />\n即係do mi so啦<br />\n咁對應C調嘅話 C major chord就會係C E G喇<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/01/184619_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F01%2F184619_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=6e6b0ca1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於minor scale就係將mi la ti降低半個音<br />\n變成咁：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/01/184716_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F01%2F184716_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f1f59ff2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同樣做法 將do mi so拎走佢地<br />\nC Eb G就會係C minor chord喇<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/01/184834_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F01%2F184834_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=38afccd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咪有種進化咗嘅感覺呢<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/01/185025_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F01%2F185025_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=86994a9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下堂如無意外就會直入主題<br />\n有唔明嘅話唔使怕醜 歡迎問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8ee33ebb4d4673ae51c251593a7e026215d5d8d","tid":724902,"uid":134968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T03:13:13.000Z","msg":"典解牙<br />\n145 係major 236 係minor 7係dim ge<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？樓主"},{"pid":"31d71c3f9059543efbefb8668e8e194f7a2d9cff","tid":724902,"uid":147789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8ee33ebb4d4673ae51c251593a7e026215d5d8d","tid":724902,"uid":134968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T03:13:13.000Z","msg":"典解牙<br />\n145 係major 236 係minor 7係dim ge<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？樓主"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T03:44:47.000Z","msg":"用琴鍵睇會明明好多<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/02/113101_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F02%2F113101_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c35a3742&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁睇你會發現3同4 7同1中間冇黑鍵<br />\n只係相隔半音<br />\n<br />\n145係major係因為do同mi係完全三度 <br />\n每粒音中間都有黑鍵相隔<br />\n<br />\n用1 chord做例子：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/02/113655_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F02%2F113655_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=93a02271&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n236嘅話 個mi會降咗半度 <br />\n因為有個位冇咗個黑鍵相隔<br />\n<br />\n用2做例子：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/02/113852_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F02%2F113852_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=7a405695&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\ndimish就比較奇妙 每粒音都係相隔兩度半<br />\n你試下數完先睇答案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n答案：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservi